com.serena.dmclient.objects
Class CMPhasePermissions

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.objects.CMPhasePermissions

public class CMPhasePermissions
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates permissions on operations that may be applied to requests when they are at certain predefined lifecycle phases.
